{"tid":24572,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[義教回饋高登]免費結他講座","createTime":"2016-12-05T15:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T08:06:50.000Z","uid":56674,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73a637811e7a42f0e5b521054b33350b121265cb","tid":24572,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"上回提要：<br />\n心態篇：<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=5890359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum5.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DMU%26message%3D5890359&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=205fafdc\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=5890359</a><br />\n練習篇：<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6135080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum5.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DMU%26message%3D6135080&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4a8e849b\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6135080</a><br />\n即興篇：<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6471148&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum7.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DMU%26message%3D6471148%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=2eb3d56e\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6471148&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n竅門篇（上）：<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum15.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6268646&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum15.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DMU%26message%3D6268646%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=20983a93\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum15.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6268646&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n<br />\n響高登寫左咁耐野，今次細佬我會為高登巴絲，搞一次免費既結他講座：<br />\n主題：流行結他（Pop），藍調結他（Blues）<br />\n程度：入門者，同樽頸者（當然你係其他都可以黎）<br />\n日期：逄星期三，六晚<br />\n時間：45分鐘<br />\n地點：葵興，地鐵站5分鐘腳程<br />\n人數：一對一，或一對二<br />\n<br />\n逄星期三晚（木結他）﹣流行結他（Pop）<br />\n﹣向全新手介紹正確起步方法<br />\n（略談CAGED system，如何運用以增加學習效率）<br />\n（基本手勢，器材準備，教材選擇解說）<br />\n﹣向樽頸者提供重拾進步之法<br />\n（一齊重新檢視以前學習既甩漏，教你點幫自己改正）<br />\n<br />\n逄星期六晚（電結他）﹣藍調結他（Blues）<br />\n﹣即興結他竅門<br />\n（淺談licks既玩法）<br />\n（做cover既方法同後續）<br />\n﹣必學經典，教材推介<br />\n<br />\n＊每節分別會有一份簡短notes提供<br />\n＊最好到時帶備自己結他，逾時不候<br />\n＊名額有限，先到先得<br />\n＊為左其他有興趣既巴絲都可以黎到，最好唔好放飛機<br />\n＊如反應熱烈會按情況加開時段<br />\n<br />\n報名表格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeJfW8eNSvSKJC9IQwtkPg6vLKShwne_b_1fcIb9B5cLPG7cA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeJfW8eNSvSKJC9IQwtkPg6vLKShwne_b_1fcIb9B5cLPG7cA%2Fviewform&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e5c754e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeJfW8eNSvSKJC9IQwtkPg6vLKShwne_b_1fcIb9B5cLPG7cA/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n之前話出既練習篇（二），等我推完呢個post先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bd43e3dc0d948b21ad3e23e9ef8cfaadb444f7","tid":24572,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"好啊,我都想請教barre chord 食指應該點發力, 因為手指公好痛呀!"},{"pid":"46772a99f314b2e3971070994da9b7abd83ac3eb","tid":24572,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"ohh 對唔住, 岩岩先係高登見到<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>Bm7好難撳要點撳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食指要一野撳唒23456線仲要配合唔到中指無名指要撳既線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得個禁字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無野可以教，最多要有個人響旁邊扶下你d手勢</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56e947fd9d29c7e94a2ed7e7010393e86da8a93","tid":24572,"uid":13561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:48:39.000Z","msg":"蘭調人都轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62eca8acf695097880826e6ee459204e8d7b7d1","tid":24572,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蘭調人都轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5019f3c1293a1bf972874b2adc4019b19a9126c5","tid":24572,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d85e41db68473153f8e7b0392cfb191495a071","tid":24572,"uid":56289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想學 0基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba8a9bf166f061388665fa03231eff6289e4c18","tid":24572,"uid":23531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"樽頸唔知點進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮撚學生冇錢跟人學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b7eaf6435f93d5906261897d4e5246d30a7a54","tid":24572,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"